Deel is your all-in-one Global People Platform

Pay anyone, anywhere in minutes

Forget multiple tools, payroll errors and unreliable reporting. Run payroll for your entire global workforce in 150 countries in one self-serve platform. 

Expand your team and hire globally

Compliantly onboard contractors and employees worldwide, without worrying about local laws, payroll and keeping up with local compliance.

Simplify, speed up, and scale global IT operations

Deel IT lets you procure, deploy, repair, and recover equipment in 130 countries without worrying about shipping, security, or damage. Plus, provision apps and create custom IT policies in a few clicks. It’s one place for all your global IT needs.

Consolidate your HR operations

With Deel HR, you can bring all of your employee data from around the world into a single global HRIS. We compliantly localize everything—from onboarding to holiday days—based on location and local labor laws.

Set your team up for success with performance tools

Drive team success and unlock powerful insights with our suite of AI-powered products to manage goals, performance, learning development, team satisfaction, and more.

Attract and retain talent with immigration support

Finding and obtaining the proper visa for a country can take months. Our immigration experts handle everything so you can relocate and retain top talent with ease.
